{"tid":1480001,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★why今日仍有大批人搶樓？】映日灣開售：代理料可即日沽清","createTime":"2019-08-17T06:25:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T06:54:58.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"27a56998444a848da955b6a258c45a68477629aa","tid":1480001,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T06:25:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190817/photo/bkn-20190817121047826-0817_00842_001_01p.jpg?20190817123933\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190817%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190817121047826-0817_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20190817123933&h=ab5dc8fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n億京發展旗下<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">荃灣映日灣周六(17日)進行首輪銷售</span></strong>，中原地產亞太區副主席兼住宅部總裁陳永傑表示，該公司客戶出席率達8成以上。客源分布方面，新界區客人佔6成，九龍及香港區客各佔2成。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，8月份大環境轉差下，樓市成交淡靜，映日灣開價有一成折讓，樓價吸引，加上間隔多元化，成功吸引市場搶購，當中有部分買家為新居屋回流客。由於剛需強烈，縱然惡劣環境，新盤亦有承接，料該盤周六公開發售的354伙可即日沽清。若項目繼續以原價加推，相信市場會有承接。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190817/bkn-20190817121047826-0817_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190817%2Fbkn-20190817121047826-0817_00842_001.html&d=9fV5YN%2BdLeg0vJDpI0pnmq3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=0389464a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190817/bkn-20190817121047826-0817_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"96ff099e51eb950beabc76274c5ac34f32a61ef0","tid":1480001,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T06:25:39.000Z","msg":"唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1be648762b70e0177f3fa5a644ed8f7e120f324e","tid":1480001,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T06:26:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/a